quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  113,1,"Say, ˹O Prophet,˺ “I seek refuge in the Lord of the daybreak"
  113,2,from the evil of whatever He has created
  113,3,and from the evil of the night when it grows dark
  113,4,and from the evil of those ˹witches casting spells by˺ blowing onto knots
  113,5,and from the evil of an envier when they envy.”